.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-8-2::.
There 2 different types of food: grapefruit, zucchini
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, writing
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, trance
There are 2 different nationalities: british, egyptian
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, ship
1. the person drinking 7up is not to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
2. the person drinking milk is not to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##8
3. the british is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
4. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
5. the person drinking 7up is not to the left of the fan of trance##8
6. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the british##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Food          | grapefruit | zucchini |
| Hobby         | skydiving  | writing  |
| Beverage           | 7up      | milk  |
| Music-Genre   | trance     | pop      |
| Nationality           | british     | egyptian    |
| Transport     | motorbike  | ship     |

