3. the fan of country is the person traveling to london##1
4. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
5. the person who likes pink is on the left of the fan of country##1
6. the person eating broccoli is not to the right of the person traveling to london##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |         2          |
| City      | colone          | london               |
| Food          | cherry       | broccoli           |
| Hobby         | baking       | drawing            |
| Color           | pink | red |
| Music-Genre   | rock         | country            |
| Transport     | helicopter   | ship               |

 